    </node>
    <node id="TGFB" maxvalue="1" input="true">
      <annotation>
        <linklist>
          <link xlink:href="uniprot:P01137"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>"Transforming growth factor beta-1
http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P01137

Multifunctional protein that controls proliferation, differentiation and other functions in many cell types.

0 = Absence of TGFB
1 = Presence of TGFB"
</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="792" y="173" style="Input"/>
    </node>
    <node id="IL6" maxvalue="1" input="true">
      <annotation>
        <linklist>
          <link xlink:href="uniprot:P05231"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>"Interleukin-6
http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P05231

cytokine involved in pro-inflammatory signaling and able to induce nerve differentiation. It has furthermore been linked to EMT in human cervical carcinoma (Miao et al 2014)


0 = IL6 Absence
1 = IL6 Presence"
</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="575" y="173" style="Input"/>
    </node>
