http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P40763

Signal transducer and transcription activator that mediates cellular responses to interleukins, KITLG/SCF, LEP and other growth factors Shuttles between the nucleus and the cytoplasm. Translocated into the nucleus upon tyrosine phosphorylation and dimerization


0 = cytoplasmic transcriptionally inactive
1 = active dimer formation and localized@nucleus"
</comment>
      </annotation>
