        <comment>"Mitogen-activated protein kinase 8
http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P45983
Mitogen-activated protein kinase 9
http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P45984

Serine/threonine-protein kinase involved in various processes such as cell proliferation, differentiation, migration, transformation and programmed cell death. Extracellular stimuli such as proinflammatory cytokines or physical stress stimulate the stress-activated protein kinase/c-Jun N-terminal kinase (SAP/JNK) signaling pathway.

0 = inactive
1 = phosphorylated active"
</comment>
      </annotation>
