http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P15884
Lymphoid enhancer-binding factor 1
http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/Q9UJU2

Participates in the Wnt signaling pathway. Activates transcription of target genes in the presence of CTNNB1."
