https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/gene/406985
microRNA 200b
https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/gene/406984
microRNA 200c
https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/gene/406983


miR200 family members are higly enriched in epithelial tisues while not present in normal fibroblast or other mesenchymal originated cells.

0 = not expressed
