          <link xlink:href="uniprot:P35222"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>"Catenin beta-1
http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P35222

Cytoplasmic when it is unstabilized (high level of phosphorylation) or bound to E-Cadherin. Binding to E-Cadherin juxtmembrane domain connect  the cadherin to the actin cytoskeleton.


0 = not @ membrane
1 = localize @ membrane"

</comment>
      </annotation>
