http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/O60716

Associates with and regulates the cell adhesion properties of both C-, E- and N-cadherins, being critical for their surface stability


0 = not @ membrane
1 = localize @ membrane"
</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="2221" y="466" style=""/>
    </node>
