        <comment>In Drosophila that FAT cadherin modulate teh Salvador/Warts/Hippo Signaling Pathway (Bennet et al. 2006). (Qi et al. 2009) showed in mice NOG8 cells that loss of FAT4 expression distrupts Hippo pathway leading to an abnormal activation of  YAP activity.
